1
00:00:00,650 --> 00:00:03,226
Imagine, if you can believe it

2
00:00:03,725 --> 00:00:07,320
A whole other world within this universe...

3
00:00:09,575 --> 00:00:16,462
In that world, people found supreme bliss in what can best be described as lucid dreams

4
00:00:17,175 --> 00:00:18,903
Reality became blurred...

5
00:00:19,925 --> 00:00:21,882
Or rather, re-defined

6
00:00:23,326 --> 00:00:25,892
But outside of their flawless reality

7
00:00:26,291 --> 00:00:29,387
The problems of the material world remained...

8
00:00:30,875 --> 00:00:35,198
And in the end, the cold, hard truths of the real world

9
00:00:35,450 --> 00:00:39,615
Caught up to them in the reality to which they had escaped

10
00:00:40,875 --> 00:00:45,440
Deep in the dark ruins, another soul who was fleeing destruction

11
00:00:45,440 --> 00:00:48,564
Discovered the final remains of this world

12
00:00:50,225 --> 00:00:55,035
These two terminals were once a means for the dreamers to manage the outside world

13
00:00:55,450 --> 00:00:58,413
Now, they form part of the mage's collection

14
00:00:59,450 --> 00:01:04,588
The mage once tried to form a world from things she had gleaned in her eclectic experience

15
00:01:05,150 --> 00:01:10,699
But as the calm observer, she never found that spark of inspiration to bring everything together

16
00:01:11,365 --> 00:01:14,176
Before fate caught up to the wandering mage

17
00:01:14,525 --> 00:01:18,077
She paid one more visit to her wise and learned friends

18
00:01:19,620 --> 00:01:21,910
She learned much during their time together

19
00:01:22,400 --> 00:01:24,384
And although she did not find the answer

20
00:01:24,925 --> 00:01:27,924
Her loneliness faded away in time

21
00:01:29,925 --> 00:01:33,881
But as she and her friends crafted other wondrous worlds together

22
00:01:34,475 --> 00:01:35,890
She finally realized

23
00:01:35,890 --> 00:01:39,191
The missing piece in the world she dreamed of creating:

24
00:01:40,717 --> 00:01:44,667
A vibrant, captivating protagonist

25
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:50,215
The glorious Traveler and their impeccable companion

26
00:01:50,215 --> 00:01:52,075
Were the perfect candidates

27
00:01:52,450 --> 00:01:54,131
She was filled with hope

28
00:01:56,071 --> 00:01:59,987
The lucid dream of a lost civilization was built anew

29
00:02:00,375 --> 00:02:05,129
And the mage's vast collection now had a world to call home

30
00:02:06,100 --> 00:02:08,250
After sojourning for so long

31
00:02:08,742 --> 00:02:12,538
It was time for her to leave lest the destruction catch up with her

32
00:02:14,037 --> 00:02:18,753
And in any case... a new story had now begun

